value.0: I... Am Owl...Spirit of Wisdom. A quiet watcher, Owl strikes without warning from the darkness. Its hidden wisdom is associated with secrets of death and the shadowy Dark Umbra. Some believe that owls themselves are spirits of the dead seeking vengeance.

I am Cockroach. I am the spirit Guide of the Warders of Man. We are both known for being cunning and surviving.  Often for those who follow me or my brood Flight is better than fighting, but we know when we must fight to survive.
I will tell you what I know... I know that those of your blood are often able to see the weavers webs at work.
The web of the weaver is what prompts the construction of items out of the materials of the wyld.
I can teach you the first gift of the tribe.. But it does not come with out cost.
All gifts you learn from the spirits will cost you spirit energy. Gnosis. But others could require you be a certain rank, or to bring the spirit an offering... Criminage...
Then the Knowledge shall be inparted to you Young Claith.
I can teach you the second gift of the tribe.. But as before it does not come with out cost.
Bring to me the Finest meal you can find... Then I shall teach you.
Then the Knowledge shall be inparted to you young warrior.
